data.description: Introducing 713 Washington St, Castroville, Texas - a charming residence that seamlessly blends the convenience of location and small-town living. This home features 3 bedrooms and 1.5 baths, providing the perfect backdrop for a cozy and inviting lifestyle. Step inside and experience the welcoming open-concept living space. As you explore further, you'll discover the allure of this property extends beyond the interior. Situated on a corner lot, the home boasts a generously sized backyard - a haven for outdoor enthusiasts. Picture yourself hosting gatherings on the large and open back porch, where you can relax and unwind in the privacy of your retreat. Parking is a breeze with the convenience of a 2-car carport, ensuring that you and your guests always have a designated space. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home or investment property. Embrace the charm of 713 Washington St and experience living in Castroville, Texas.
